instructions: put the charger on the table cloth
put the fork to the left of the charger with prongs pointing upward
put the dinner knife to the right of the charger with the blade pointing upward
put the salad fork next to the dinner fork with prongs pointing upward
put the salad knife next to the dinner knife with blade pointing upward
put the soup spoon next to the salad knife with bowl pointing upward
put the dessert spoon above the charger with bowl pointing left
put the dessert fork below the dessert spoon with prongs facing right
put the bread plate to the left of the table cloth
put the butter knife diagonally on the bread plate with blade first
put the water glass to the right of the table cloth
put the napkin in the center of the plate
